                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi>115.) I was with Kennerley—I did not see the prisoner take the handkerchief, but I saw him run away—he threw down the handkerchief, and I took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I am quite innocent. I am a hard-working boy, as you may see by my hands.</p>
